# Digital Products Ideas

> One-time purchase products that create passive/semi-passive income streams.

---

## Why Digital Products?

**The Appeal:**
- Create once, sell forever
- No inventory, no shipping
- Near-100% profit margin after creation
- Can complement consulting/services

**The Reality:**
- Requires marketing effort to sell
- Competition is fierce
- "Passive" still requires support/updates
- Takes time to build audience

**Best Approach:** Build products that solve problems you've already solved for clients.

---

