### Product Definition

**What:** Curated collection of professional-grade Claude Code resources

| Component | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| Price | $49-99 (or $9-19/mo subscription) |
| Format | GitHub repo access or downloadable ZIP |
| Audience | Developers using Claude Code professionally |

### Potential Contents

**Skills:**
- Code review skill (language-agnostic)
- Feature development workflow
- Tech debt analyzer
- Debug methodology
- Design system implementation guide

**Slash Commands:**
- Task management workflow
- Git commit assistant
- PR review automation
- Documentation generator

**Subagents:**
- Research agents
- Code analysis agents
- Documentation agents

**CLAUDE.md Templates:**
- Global constitution template
- Project-specific templates
- Folder-level patterns
- Stack-specific templates (React, NestJS, Python)

### Viability Assessment

| Factor | Assessment |
|--------|------------|
| Viability | Medium |
